title: High school football recap
text: High school football - Week 5 takeaways October 11, 2015 | Doug Bonjour Here are 10 takeaways from week five of high school football in southwest Connecticut. Mark Conrad / For Hearst Connecticut Media 1 of 11 10. TAKING A SEAT: Only eight of the FCIAC's 17 schools played this weekend. A few teams, including 3-0 New Canaan, were off for the second time in just five weeks. Isn't the point of playing football to, you know, actually play?
